1
00:00:00,680 --> 00:00:02,360
Remember...
牢記

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,280
There must be something that you always wanted to do but you couldn't.
一定有什麼想做但一直做不到的事情吧

3
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,880
There are many things I want to do.
我有很多想做的事

4
00:00:07,960 --> 00:00:08,880
Very good.
很好

5
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:10,760
Whatever it is, however it is done,
不管是什麼事  無論要怎樣做

6
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:12,880
you will start doing it with utmost planning.
都要以做計畫開始

7
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:16,160
You should have daily, weekly, monthly plans.
應該有每日，每周，每月的計劃

8
00:00:16,240 --> 00:00:19,000
You won't cut corners. You'll make it complicated.
不要走捷徑，要把事情做細緻

9
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:28,400
Dad, don't you remember anything?
爺爺  你不記得了嗎？

10
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:33,480
Dad, I'm getting a divorce.
爸  我要離婚了

11
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:35,280
I'll introduce you to someone.
我給你介紹一個人

12
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:36,840
But that's how he works.
但這就是他的工作方式

13
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:41,160
- Who is he? - That charlatan journalist, Ates Arbay.
-他是誰？-那個卑鄙的記者Ates Arbay

14
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:44,640
I used to be a fiery and an idealist reporter.
我曾經是一個熱情的理想主義者

15
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,840
Oh, poor Agah.
哦，可憐的Agah.

16
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,080
What have you done?
你做了什麼？

17
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,800
AFTER 2 AM - CUSTOMERS LEAVE - THE DOORS ARE LOCKED
淩晨2點之後 -顧客離開 -鎖門

18
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,120
LIFE BEGINS SIGNED: AGAH BEYOGLU
簽名：AGAH BEYOGLU

19
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,640
What do I do with him now?
我現在該怎麼辦？

20
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:20,240
They had "Nevra" written on their foreheads. What's with that?
他們的額頭上寫著“Nevra”，這是怎麼回事？

21
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:23,160
Just a coincidence. It has nothing to do with me.
隻是巧合  與我無關

22
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:27,280
Selim, I actually have a question.
Selim，我有一個問題

23
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,400
Do you know someone named Naimhan Turedi?
你知道有人叫Naimhan Turedi嗎？

24
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:33,320
- Naimhan... - Turedi. Born in Kambura.
-Naimhan- Turedi出生於Kambura

25
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,160
Oh yes, of course I do.
哦，是的，我知道

26
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:38,920
Yasin used to collect trash over by the garage. He's dead now.
Yasin以前經常在車庫裏收集垃圾  他已經死了

27
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:44,440
They had sons. Not good for anything.
他們有個兒子，冇什麼用處

28
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,400
They all left for Istanbul.
他們都去了伊斯坦佈爾

29
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,840
How about someone named Mehmet Yurtgil? A judge.
叫Mehmet Yurtgil的法官怎麼樣？

30
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:54,560
- He was assigned to here? - No. He might've passed by, though.
-他被分配到這裏嗎？-不，他可能已經過身了

31
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,680
I don't remember the name.
我不記得這個名字

32
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,280
Alright.
好的

33
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:06,280
I'll speak to the guys over at the station.
我要去跟警局的人聊一聊

34
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:10,120
Come by again, though, this time for dinner.
晚上過來吃飯

35
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:13,240
Don't even think about going back before stopping by one last time.
你不來的話就別想回去

36
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,400
Sure.
好的

37
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,800
Where's Agah Beyoglu? He's my dad. Where's my dad?
Agah Beyoglu在哪裏，他是我父親

38
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,160
He was discharged.
他出院了

39
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:32,280
Discharged? When?
出院了？什麼時候？

40
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,920
He was right there when I went to sleep. I wake up and he's gone.
我睡覺的時候他就在那裏，我醒來之後他就不見了

41
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,960
When was he discharged?
他什麼時候出院的？

42
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:41,680
Ms. Zuhal, your father left in a hurry. He left you a note.
Zuhal女士，您的父親匆忙離開，他給您留了張紙條

43
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:49,200
- Dad? - Over here.
-爸爸？-在這

44
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:51,080
What are you doing, dad?
爸  你在做什麼？

45
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,240
How about I don't share the details?
我不分享細節怎麼樣？

46
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,680
What is this note? Huh?
這是什麼紙條？

47
00:04:57,760 --> 00:05:00,560
"I'm going to get the car. See you at the house."
“我要去取車，家裏見”

48
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:04,240
We were worried sick. You should've let us know.
我們都很擔心你，你應該讓我們知道的

49
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:08,720
I'm not used to letting people know.
我不習慣讓別人知道

50
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:13,720
I haven't been letting anyone know anything since your mother died.
自從你母親過身以來，我一直冇有讓任何人知道任何事情

51
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,240
That's some excuse!
那是個借口！

52
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:19,680
We were worried sick about you! How about some thoughtfulness?
我們真的很擔心你！考慮下我們好嗎？

53
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:26,360
You should really stop shouting. I can't hear you anyway.
別喊了，反正我也聽不見

54
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,680
KILLER OR VICTIM?
是殺手還是受害者？

55
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:50,320
KAMBURA POLICE DEPARTMENT
KAMBURA警察署

56
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,000
Nevra? Welcome!
Nevra！歡迎！

57
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,240
It's me, Vural.
是我，Vural

58
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:09,320
- Vural? - See?
-Vural -你看

59
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:12,520
Once someone leaves Kambura, they forget all about their past.
一旦有人離開了Kambura，他們就把以前的事情都忘了

60
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,960
You're hurting me.
你太傷我心了

61
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,280
- Vural. - Yes, Vural.
-Vural -是的，Vural

62
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,560
Sorry, didn't recognize you.
抱歉，冇認出你

63
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:24,240
Of course not. Istanbul is another world.
當然了，伊斯坦佈爾是另一個世界

64
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:27,960
We've been reading all about you on the newspapers, though.
不過，我們一直在報紙上看有關你的消息

65
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:32,000
I saw you driving earlier today, but you were gone before I could say hi.
我看到你今天早些時候在開車，但在我打招呼之前你走了

66
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,080
Welcome.
歡迎

67
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,000
Thanks.
謝謝

68
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:41,320
- How's Aunt Nesrin doing? Well, I hope? - Sure.
-Nesrin姨媽過得好嗎？-很好

69
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,160
Don't you worry. I'll take care of it.
放心吧，我會自己修的

70
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,760
Excuse me?
什麼？

71
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,600
Your door. I'll get it fixed.
車門，我會自己修的

72
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,760
What a shame.
真抱歉

73
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,400
I can take care of it.
我來修吧

74
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,480
Come on...
算了……

75
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:15,520
You're not coming back to Kambura anytime soon.
你不會很快回來Kambura的

76
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,000
You shouldn't.
你不會的

77
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,120
At least let me pay for it.
至少讓我付錢給你吧

78
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:24,080
Your money's no good here.
你的錢在這裏冇有用

79
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:28,680
- Anyway, goodbye. - Goodbye.
-總之，再見了 -再見

80
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:44,080
Agah! Come out!
Agah！出來！

81
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:53,000
Isn't Istanbul real expensive? How can you make it with your salary?
伊斯坦佈爾房價不是很貴嗎？薪水怎麼可能付得起？

82
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,000
I make do.
我付得起

83
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:59,160
Any information?
有任何信息嗎？

84
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:03,520
Can't find anything. He left Kambura a long time ago.
什麼都找不到  他很久以前就離開了Kambura

85
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,440
It's been years.
已經好幾年了

86
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,640
No info whatsoever since they've left.
從他們離開之後，冇有任何信息

87
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:12,240
But I'll tell the guys to keep looking.
但是我會告訴大家繼續尋找

88
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,200
We'll let you know if we have something.
如果有消息我們會通知您

89
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:19,160
So how do you make it? Do you rent your place?
那你怎麼做的？租房子嗎？

90
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
Agah!

91
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,920
Come out!
出來！

92
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:29,200
Agah! You can't hide from me!
Agah！你躲不過我！

93
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,600
I'll burn this whole place down!
我會把整個地方都燒掉！

94
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,760
Come on, join us.
來吧，我們一起吃

95
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,160
So...
那麼……

96
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,400
Does Kambura feel any different?
Kambura有什麼變化嗎

97
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,280
Not at all. It's exactly the same.
完全冇有，還是老樣子

98
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:02,520
I recall when you used to be a little girl.
我記得你小時候

99
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,480
How old were you?
你那時候幾歲？

100
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,600
Ten.
十

101
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:10,120
I've been courting your mom ever since then. She's never interested.
從那以後我一直在嚮你媽媽示愛，她一直不感興趣

102
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,240
I'm not surprised.
意料之中

103
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,720
I'll kill you.
我要殺了你

104
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,080
You're being too much.
你太過分了

105
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,960
Salih...

106
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,040
Come on, let me go.
好了，讓我走吧

107
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,200
We can go our separate ways.
我們可以各走各的

108
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:26,920
Besides, you're wounded. Don't let it get infected.
另外你受傷了，小心感染

109
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,080
You're the one who shot me, you lunatic!
是你先開槍打我，你個瘋子！

110
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:32,280
It was a mistake! It was an accident!
那是誤會，純屬意外！

111
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,560
You shot me point blank! How is that an accident?
你直接嚮我開了槍！怎麼會是意外呢？

112
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:39,600
How did you find me? Have you been following me?
你是怎麼找到我的？你一直在跟蹤我嗎？

113
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,520
Why would I be following you?
我為什麼要跟蹤你？

114
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:45,360
My car broke down and you were the first car to come by!
我的車壞了，你是第一輛駛來的車！

115
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,800
It was a coincidence! It was fate!
真是巧合！是天意！

116
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:50,600
I'm putting the gun away.
我把槍收起來

117
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,560
See?
看到？

118
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,040
I've put it away. See?
我把槍收起來了，看到了嗎？

119
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:59,400
Come on, you put yours away, as well, Salih.
好了，你也把你的收起來吧，Salih

120
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,840
Salih...

121
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:09,440
Come over and let's talk, brother to brother. 
過來，讓我們聊一聊

122
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,400
Come on.
來吧

123
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:16,520
Remember our conversations back in Kambura?
還記得我們在Kambura的談話嗎？

124
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:20,720
You're like a brother to me. Come on, don't do this.
你就像我的兄弟，來吧，別這樣

125
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,560
Salih...

126
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:27,240
I used to go to the post office every day. Just to see your mom.
我以前每天去郵局隻是為了看看你媽媽

127
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,960
I used to send fake letters.
我曾經寄假信件

128
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,920
But I never got the chance to meet her.
但是我一直冇有機會見到她

129
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:35,120
One day, they told me she'd left.
突然有一天，他們告訴我她已經離開了

130
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:40,240
It had only been six or seven months since she'd started here.
她來這裏才六、七個月

131
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:45,240
- She left so soon. - It was a year. We stayed for a year.
-她這麼快就走了 -一年，我們住了一年

132
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:47,040
Give or take.
差不多吧

133
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:52,680
I never got to meet her then, but I got her in the end, after all.
之後再冇見到過她，但最終我還是得到了

134
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,240
It's delicious.
很好吃

135
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,840
Enjoy.
吃吧

136
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:06,000
Salih...
薩利赫

137
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:14,240
Come on, let's have a chat. We're brothers.
來吧，我們聊聊吧，好兄弟

138
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,240
Salih...

139
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,560
Tell me, why?
告訴我為什麼？

140
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,400
Why did you come after me after all these years?
這麼多年過去了，你為什麼要找我？

141
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,560
Why did you try to kill me?
你為什麼要殺我？

142
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,760
What did I do to you?
我對你做了什麼？

143
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,080
That's funny.
真好笑

144
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:39,400
- That's what Naimhan asked. - Naimhan?
-那也是Naimhan問的問題 -Naimhan？

145
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,600
What did you do to him?
你對他做了什麼？

146
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,880
What did you do to Naimhan?
你對Naimhan做了什麼？

147
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,880
Tell me!
告訴我！

148
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:52,000
Salih, if this is the end of the road...
薩利赫，如果這是我的終點……

149
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,160
Then let me do it.
那就讓我自己來吧

150
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:58,680
- Drop your gun. Drop it! - I'm not dropping it.
-放下槍！-我不會放的

151
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,520
I'll fuck you up! Drop it!
你他媽的快放下！

152
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:04,440
I won't let you die before telling me why you tried to kill me.
在告訴我為什麼要殺我之前，我不會讓你死

153
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,080
Tell me, why!
告訴我為什麼！

154
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,200
Why were you after me?
你為什麼找我？

155
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,200
Conscience.
良心

156
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,880
Conscience?
良心？

157
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:16,840
What conscience? What does that have to do with anything?
什麼良心？良心和這有什麼關係？

158
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:20,960
You know what conscience means, don't you?
你知道什麼是良心，對嗎？

159
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,160
Fuck you and your conscience!
去尼瑪的良心！

160
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,840
You won't look me in the eye?
你都不好好看我一眼嗎？

161
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,320
It's been three years.
已經三年了

162
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:56,040
You haven't come to visit for three whole years.
你已經三年冇來了

163
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,560
You kicked me out.
你把我踢出去的

164
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,560
You haven't even called.
你甚至都冇有打電話

165
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,440
You told me not to.
你告訴我不要打

166
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:08,440
I did, because you left that cushy job and went and became a cop!
是啊，因為你辭掉了那份輕鬆的工作，去當警察了!

167
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,800
What was all that education for?
這些教育是為了什麼？

168
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:15,000
See what it's come to?
你看現在怎麼樣？

169
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,040
You might've gotten yourself into trouble.
你會惹上麻煩的

170
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:21,800
Your name, written on the foreheads of dead men.
你的名字，寫在死者的額頭上

171
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,120
Nevra...

172
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:28,120
I worked my ass off to get you through school.
我努力工作供你上學

173
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:32,800
I had to work as a cashier in addition to my day job.
我除了日常工作外還要做出納員

174
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,960
When that didn't do it...
但當那些冇起作用的時候…

175
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,640
You got married four times.
你結了四次婚

