384
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:26,120
A miserable soul, desperate for attention.
一個悲慘的靈魂，渴望得到關註

385
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:31,320
The biggest favor you can do for such a sociopath is to talk about him.
你能為這樣的反社會變態做的最大的幫助就是談論他

386
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:35,640
But you've been on this case ever since the murders started.
但是，自謀殺案發生以來，您一直在關註這個案件

387
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,640
Isn't that a favor to him, then?
那不是對他有利嗎？

388
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,400
