You left the house.
你離開了家

482
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:03,120
I used to pray with all my might not to get sick.
我曾經盡力祈禱不生病

483
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:06,240
Not to get fevers so that my father didn't get mad at me.
不要發燒，這樣我的父親就不會生我的氣

484
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:08,560
You didn't look after mom, either.
你也冇照顧媽媽

485
