I'll be right there.
我馬上到

509
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,160
Hand these out to the guys.
把這些交給他們

510
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,880
Alright...
好了……

511
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,000
Where's Nevra?
Nevra呢？

512
