She got a tip from somewhere. She went to the courthouse to look into it.
她從某個地方得到了線報，去了法院進行調查

513
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:04,000
You know Mehmet Yurtgil, the judge?
你知道Mehmet Yurtgil嗎？

514
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,640
He was known for taking bribes.
他因受賄而聞名

515
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,240
She's looking into the suspects that were wronged.
她在調查被冤枉的嫌疑犯

516
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:11,960
She thinks someone might've took revenge on him.
她認為有人可能會對他報仇

517
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:14,520
Alright then. Anyway,
好吧，不管怎樣

518
00:37:15,080 --> 00:37:18,240
